bNTI.ghost.RC.part.TP.TREAT$Treatment<-factor(bNTI.ghost.RC.part.TP.TREAT$Treatment, levels= c("Control", "Pre_flowering_drought", "Post_flowering_drought"), labels = c("CON", "PRE", "POST"))

ggplot(bNTI.ghost.RC.part.TP.TREAT[bNTI.ghost.RC.part.TP.TREAT$Treatment=="CON",], aes(x = factor(TP), y = Value ,fill=bNTI.ghost.RC.partition)) +
  geom_bar(stat='identity', position = "fill")+  ###add <   > for relative abundance
  labs(x="Week",y = "Relative importance")+
  facet_wrap(~Habitat, ncol = 4,strip.position= 'left')+
  theme(strip.text = element_text(size = 15,face="bold"),
        panel.spacing = unit(0, "lines"),
        legend.title = element_text(colour="black", size=15, face="bold"),
        legend.text = element_text(colour="black", size=15, face="bold"),
        axis.text=element_text(size=10,face="bold",angle = 90),
        axis.title=element_text(size=15,face="bold"))+
  scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent)+
  scale_fill_manual(values= col11) + guides(fill=FALSE)
